@node "Hist" "History of DMS-Window" 

==========================================================================

 DMS-Window is Based on "DImp-Win V1.20."  The Intuition Interface for 
 Disk Imploder which was also written by me. Although I still consider DImp 
 to be the superior disk archiver for the Amiga I can't see everyone
 changing over to it. This is the result of me being forced to use DMS.      
 
 DMS-Window was written in assembly language using the Macro68 assembler.

 Special thanks to Greg Macdonald for many suggestions, bug testing and 
 programming help.

 If you have any suggestions or bug reports then please contact me at the
 address below.

==========================================================================
 
@endnode
